### Mautic Series

7.0.x series

### Mautic installed version

7.0.1

### Way of installing

I downloaded a release from https://www.mautic.org/mautic-releases

### PHP version

8.3.6

### What browsers are you seeing the problem on?

Firefox

### What happened?

I encountered a bug when configuring SugarCRM plugin settings. On the contact and company mapping page, when clicking on the page selector buttons at the bottom, nothing happens. As such, I can only edit the first 20-something integration fields. Below is the HTTP request that was sent when I clicked on the page selector button.

{
  "log": {
    "version": "1.2",
    "creator": { "name": "Firefox", "version": "141.0" },
    "entries": [
      {
        "startedDateTime": "2026-03-23T15:49:57.525+08:00",
        "request": {
          "method": "POST",
          "url": "https://your-mautic-site.com/s/ajax?action=plugin:getIntegrationFields",
          "httpVersion": "HTTP/1.1",
          "headers": [
            { "name": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8" },
            { "name": "X-Requested-With", "value": "XMLHttpRequest" }
          ],
          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
            "params": [
              { "name": "page", "value": "2" },
              { "name": "integration", "value": "Sugarcrm" },
              { "name": "settings[object]", "value": "lead" }
            ],
            "text": "page=2&integration=Sugarcrm&settings%5Bobject%5D=lead&settings%5Bintegration%5D=Sugarcrm"
          }
        },
        "response": {
          "status": 200,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"success\":0}"
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}



### How can we reproduce this issue?

Step 1: Install and enable the SugarCRM integration.

Step 2. Navigate to Plugins > SugarCRM > Contact Mapping.

Step 3. Attempt to click the "2" or any other button among the page selector buttons at the bottom of the list.

Step 4. Nothing happens.

